description: OFFER ACCEPTED - OPEN HOUSES CANCELED.......................Welcome to 724 East 2nd Street, one of the finest blocks on the East Side! Completed in 2017 by a renowned South Boston Developer, this Stunning Penthouse offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms and 2 PRIVATE DECKS! Soaring ceilings greet you, leading way to a sophisticated top-floor oasis offering a perfect layout. The chef's kitchen boasts Viking appliances, Caesarstone counters, and a wine fridge. The oversized living and dining area features an elegant gas fireplace and abundant natural light.  Easy access to both private outdoor spaces… PRIVATE DECK & ROOFDECK!  Modern amenities include a Video Doorbell, Nest thermostat, and Sonos in-ceiling speakers. The master suite includes a large WIC and luxurious en-suite bath. Additional features include two well-sized bedrooms, an office nook/mud area, and a large storage locker in the basement. 1 year of PREPAID RENTAL PARKING is included.
